"Shook Ones Part II" (also stylised as "Shook Ones Pt. II") is a song by American hip hop group Mobb Deep. It served as the lead single from their 1995 album The Infamous. The song is a sequel to the group's 1994 promotional single "Shook Ones", with similar lyrics, but less profanity. The original song is featured on the b-side of some releases of "Shook Ones Part II". The song is told from the perspective of inner-city youths engaged in territorial warfare and struggling for financial gains.
